title: TAYLER HOLDER SPEAKS ON SOMMER RAY CHARLY JORDAN DRAMA -- BFFs EP. 32
description:
Tayler Holder joins our Miami interview series to discuss the recent comments by Sommer Ray on another podcast, his transition into becoming an artist, and talk about his upcoming fight this weekend with AnEsonGib.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
